<div id="section">
<h2>Vision</h2>
<p>
Shalamar Hospital will distinguish itself as a leader in re-defining health care 
delivery and will be recognized for its services and facilities in providing quality 
and innovative care to the patients. It is our mission to serve the community by 
providing quality patient care and services to all patients and their families.</p>
 
<h3>Mission</h3>
It is our mission to serve the community by providing quality patient care and services 
to all patients and their families. We are committed to provide and continuously improve 
our facilities and expertise to provide those services. We will improve community health 
by providing an environment that is state-of-the-art, safe, efficient, cost effective, 
team- oriented, respectful and compassionate.To accomplish our Mission, we focus on 
three objectives:

1)Recruit, value, develop, and celebrate an outstanding team of employees who possess 
clinical skills and expertise, and above all, possess the core value of Caring for others

2) Develop and maintain strong physician-patient partnerships centered on patient care, 
open communications, and mutually accountable performance.

3) Continuously review and serve the unique health care needs of the community.
</p>
